50:15.303 --> 50:18.181
Loki, what are you doing?

50:19.016 --> 50:20.392
I know what I want.

50:23.854 --> 50:26.064
I know what kind of god I need to be...

50:28.775 --> 50:29.776
for you.

50:31.820 --> 50:33.030
For all of us.

50:34.239 --> 50:38.660
<i>And when he steps into
the Temporal Loom and sacrifices himself,</i>

50:38.660 --> 50:41.788
I think that's a moment
