50:49.212 --> 50:51.298
There was a draft of the script

50:51.298 --> 50:53.050
of the very end, the very end.

50:53.050 --> 50:55.677
Something wasn't sitting right
with both of us about it.

50:55.677 --> 50:59.306
<i>And the issue was, this draft
didn't have Loki destroying the Loom.</i>

50:59.306 --> 51:03.018
<i>He saved the Loom from imploding
