51:50.440 --> 51:53.026
<i>That was a pretty epic sort of moment.</i>

51:58.615 --> 52:01.993
<i>Tonally, that was
a very tough costume to land on</i>

52:01.993 --> 52:05.163
because it needed
to have a monastic quality,

52:05.914 --> 52:11.002
but he also has a history
of wanting the throne, to be a king.

52:11.002 --> 52:14.005
And he's kind of
positioning himself to be

52:14.005 --> 52:18.301
looking over everything
in the manner of a king, but humble.

52:21.847 --> 52:24.683
<i>And humbled by the weight
of that responsibility,</i>

52:24.683 --> 52:29.187
so it's just figuring out how that costume
