52:34.359 --> 52:37.529
- The grand finale.
- The grand finale of <i>Loki.</i>

52:37.529 --> 52:39.364
- Yeah.
- Seasons 1 and 2.

52:39.364 --> 52:43.243
<i>It's resonant, it's moving,
'cause he's been through so much.</i>

52:43.243 --> 52:47.038
<i>And so much struggle
