52:48.832 --> 52:50.792
<i>So many questions.</i>

52:50.792 --> 52:54.838
And to sort of come back,
it feels like it's

52:54.838 --> 52:58.258
a reacceptance of something.

52:58.258 --> 53:01.553
Or a redefinition of himself, somehow.

53:01.553 --> 53:03.930
And I think it's interesting
that from the beginning,

53:03.930 --> 53:06.183
we always talked,
