55:16.646 --> 55:19.149
There was a huge opportunity here

55:19.149 --> 55:21.860
to show a character evolve

55:21.860 --> 55:25.530
from being petty to being
someone who sacrifices for others

55:25.530 --> 55:27.532
<i>and feels the value of that.</i>

55:27.532 --> 55:31.328
And to tell that story,
