55:47.469 --> 55:51.973
<i>And then that came from wanting
to tell a story</i>

55:51.973 --> 55:54.726
<i>that had, like, a mythic weight to it,</i>

55:54.726 --> 55:58.730
<i>that's befitting the Norse mythology
