56:42.190 --> 56:46.277
And I feel so fortunate
and so grateful to the audience

56:46.277 --> 56:48.363
<i>'cause people really
seem to be interested</i>

56:48.363 --> 56:51.282
<i>in the ideas and the characters
and the world and the TVA</i>

56:51.282 --> 56:55.036
<i>and the performances and all these
great new actors in the MCU.</i>

56:55.036 --> 56:59.416
<i>So, my feeling
is one of immense gratitude and,</i>

57:00.250 --> 57:03.628
to be completely honest,
profound excitement.
